reviews.text:
One of the best hidden gems for pan fried grouper meat with flat rice noodles.
The Borscht is amazingly good, baked porkchop with rice is not as good as it used to be, but still a good try.
dry fried beef river? Great
Famous but quality is just fair

Quick and decent breakfast sets.  I like the yangzhou fried rice, which I have packed home a few times.

Returned here a  couple of months later.  Had the western set for $40 plus a cold tea.  The beef was okay though had lots of fat.
Good quality local food, some local specialties not found elsewhere

result.name: 金城餐廳

reviews.text: 啫啫雞煲同豉椒鮮魷炒麵非常好昧道
三餸晚餐連蒸花尾都不過三百元，非常抵食。
地方不豪華，但食物有質素
當天龍躉炒河缺貨。點了招牌摩囉雞扒飯，不過不失。下午茶魚柳茶餐配金磚(西多士)$43 魚柳有點濕，不夠乾身。
豉椒龍躉飯 招牌焗豬扒飯 連中西湯各一 值得一試
